The MobileNetV2 weights distributed within the trained model checkpoint
(.h5 file) in this repository have been fine-tuned from the original
ImageNet-pretrained weights. Modifications include: unfreezing and
retraining the final 10 convolutional layers on the Flickr8k caption
dataset as part of an end-to-end image-captioning model.

This product was trained on the Flickr8k dataset:

    Hodosh, M., Young, P., & Hockenmaier, J. (2013). Framing image
    description as a ranking task: Data, models and evaluation metrics.
    Journal of Artificial Intelligence Research, 47, 853-899.

The Flickr8k dataset is provided by its authors for non-commercial
research and educational use only. The individual photographs remain
under the copyright of their original Flickr authors. No Flickr8k
images are redistributed in this repository.

Evaluation uses the SPICE metric from the pycocoevalcap package:

    Anderson, P., Fernando, B., Johnson, M., & Gould, S. (2016).
    SPICE: Semantic Propositional Image Caption Evaluation.
    arXiv:1607.08822.
